Instructions:

Step 1: Select a file by pressing the "Select Files to Convert button"

Step 2: Confirm the layout of your PDF in the Preview PDF section (At the top of the application).

Step 3: If you would like to change/fix anything press the EDIT button and select your default text editor (Notepad on windows, jedit on linux, SimpleText on mac).

Step 4: When finished editing, save the file then press the Convert Selected Files button; to repreview the edited document reselect the file i.e. return to Step 1.